		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MMC1 is MMC1=Random, MMC1A has non-random with no WRAM disable I think then MMC1B2 I know always boots in bank F. But don't take my word, check the docs. I check kevs for MMC1 stuff for development like that.

		

